1. HTML tags are not just tags but it denotes a meaning to it.
   Like h1 means that the heading is the Main heading of the page.

2. Structure of an HTML page looks like:
                           HTML
                          /    \
                      head      body
                     /   \      /   \
                  title  meta  h1   p ..........etc

3. Use google dev blog to see the meta tags information as it will be useful
   to rank the website using Google SEO.
4. Always close the tags in HTML as it will be a good practice and will
   be beneficial when we will be doing JS and React JS.
5. Some tags have compulsory attributes. like a tag has href="" attribute.
